description: Trench Metals Corp. operates as a mineral exploration and development company in Canada. It has an option agreement to acquire a 100% interest in the Gorilla Lake uranium project covering 7,000 hectares located in the Athabasca basin of Northern Saskatchewan; and Higginson Lake Uranium project covering an area of approximately 2,312 hectares located in Athabasca, Saskatchewan. The company was formerly known as Trench Solutions Inc. and changed its name to Trench Metals Corp. in November 2020. Trench Metals Corp. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
